 Zero coupon bonds and spot rate
 Floating-rate notes
 Interpreting bond yields
 Bond yields and term structure of interest rates
 Bond price volatility: duration, convexity and theta
 Treasury and agency securities markets
 Corporate debt instruments
Securitization:
 Residential mortgage loans
 Mortgage pass-through securities and commercial MBSs
 CMOs
 Asset-backed securities
 CDOs
Derivatives:
 Analysis of bonds with embedded options
 Convertible bonds
 Interest rate futures and options
 Interest rate swaps and agreements
 Credit derivatives
Mathematical modeling:
 Fitting the yield curves
 Vasicek and Cox, Ingersoll and Ross term structure models
 Credit risk modeling




